An agent, or drug, that promotes venous drainage.
A substance that is poisonous to worms.

column4: Strictly, a substance intended to kill pests. In common usage, any substance used for controlling, preventing, or destroying animal, microbiological or plant pests.

Something that causes vertigo, or dizziness, especially because of great height.
